persons:
    person-frenya-spearwife:
        properties:
            name:
                value: "Frenya"
            gender: female
        notes: "One of six spearwives accompanying Mance Rayder (as Abel) to Winterfell. Described as having a thick waist and enormous breasts; wore a girdle of hempen rope wound from hips to breasts. During the escape attempt at the Battlements Gate she kills the second guard with his own spear. She stays behind on the drawbridge to fight the pursuing guards alone — holding them so Theon and Jeyne can reach the outer battlements. Fate unknown but presumed captured or killed. (ADWD, 'Theon')"
